  <title translate="true">MT-POP-Indexer-Defintions</title>
  <keywords>
    <keyword translate="true">Indexer</keyword>
  </keywords>
  <body>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="1" colcount="1" style="width:450px;">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">A commercially </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Indexer</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> is a cam device with input and output-shafts. When the Input-shaft rotates continuously, the output-shaft indexes progressively. After a number of index motions, the output shaft returns to its original position. </text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#343400;" /></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">Some definitions that are used with Indexers:</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Number-of-Stops</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">: number-of times the output-shaft must index to make one complete rotation.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Index-Angle</text><text styleclass="Popup Box2" translate="true">:</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> rotational angle of the index-motion of the output-shaft.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box" style="text-align:center;"><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Index Angle (degrees) = 360 / Number-of-Stops</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Index-Period</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">: rotational angle of the input-shaft to complete the </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Index-Angle</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> of the output-shaft.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Dwell-Period</text><text styleclass="Popup Box2" translate="true">:</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> rotational angle of the input-shaft to complete the </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Dwell</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">. </text></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box2" style="text-align:center;"><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Index-Period + Dwell-Period = 360°</text></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
  </body>
</topic>
